sentences.sentence: Investigate the clinical efficacy of proximal needling and ventouse treating lumbar gluteal myofascitis.
sentences.translation: 探讨采用傍针刺加拔火罐法治疗腰臀肌筋膜炎的临床疗效。
这个症状叫臀肌失忆症。
